<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of the implementation of Article 7 (b) and (c), the Commission shall be assisted by a Committee composed of the representatives of the Member States and chaired by the representative of the Commission. </inglise>
